      } ${invoiceCs} ${ctx.ND} ${deliveryDateYyyyMmDd}-XXXXXX-V1.motn`;

      // --------------- SPECS FOLDERS IN A5 X-PRODUCTION FOLDER

      // xa5FolderInXProdution

      // 20220216 DIONÍSIO XDWFA221003
      const {
